14:29:32.547 [INFO] - `00_inbox/`: unprocessed drops and requests
14:29:32.547 [INFO] - `10_entities/cast/`: canonical people, pets, and named systems
14:29:32.547 [INFO] - `20_work/`: reminders and active tasks
14:29:32.547 [INFO] - `30_knowledge/`: capture, notes, and threads
14:29:32.547 [INFO] - `40_projects/`: concrete project folders and artifacts; folder names start with the project creation date as `YYYY_MM_DD_`, and the canonical project record is `README.MD` inside each folder
14:29:32.547 [INFO] - `50_finance/`: invoices and purchases
14:29:32.547 [INFO] - `60_outbox/`: channel trust docs, drafts, and outbound state
14:29:32.547 [INFO] - `90_memory/`: assistant memory and story/history surfaces
