14:29:32.547 [INFO] - Read nested `AGENTS.MD` files when you enter a folder.
14:29:32.547 [INFO] - Before starting task work, inspect `99_system/` with `tree` and then read the relevant workflow or schema docs there.
14:29:32.547 [INFO] - Records are gradually migrating toward YAML frontmatter so they stay easy to browse in Obsidian while carrying structured fields for automation.
14:29:32.547 [INFO] - The migration period can be a little messy in the short term because older notes and newer structured notes may coexist, but the long-term goal is to streamline the workspace and clean up record handling.
