14:29:32.547 [INFO] - Entity files in `10_entities/cast/` are authoritative for identity, `primary_contact_email` when present, and birthdays when present.
14:29:32.547 [INFO] - If the relevant canonical file does not show the needed fact, ask for clarification instead of guessing.
14:29:32.547 [INFO] - Keep changes focused and preserve lane boundaries across household, day job, client, startup, and hobby contexts.

